#: app/settings.php:178
msgid "Hippoo! is not just a shop management app, it's also a platform that enables you to extend its capabilities. With the ability to install extensions, you can customize your experience and add new features to the app. Browse and install other Hippoo plugins from our app to enhance your store's functionality."
